{"type": "article", "id": 53835, "title": "这些造型简练的户外灯，是夏夜聚会上的好帮手｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-31T23:11:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 17751, "name": "Alki"}, {"id": 50766, "name": "Up Front"}, {"id": 20020, "name": "Rooms"}, {"id": 47966, "name": "Carl Hansen & Son"}, {"id": 50767, "name": "Ian Bok"}, {"id": 50768, "name": "Iratzoki Lizaso"}, {"id": 18615, "name": "Freytag Anderson"}, {"id": 37273, "name": "Brad Ascalon"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 177, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180531223948N9QSOuZXjmawWki1.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: #657ab7} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>June Outdoor Lighting Collection by Emiliana Design Studio for Vibia</h3><p>西班牙灯具品牌 Vibia 的灯具，一般都采用较单一的基本色调来设计，用照明来带出专属于空间氛围的好品味。比如这组最新推出的 June 户外灯系列，希望能够成为夏日夜晚聚会的主角。</p><p>June 系列的灵感来自中国传统灯笼，但 Emiliana 设计工作室用更现代风格的设计语言进行表达，加入月亮的形状，散发出温暖的光芒。整个系列包括悬挂式吊灯、台灯、落地灯以及便携式悬挂灯 4 种款式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224017Slj9KhoasT6Qc0qf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.012500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224018aUf7XgItlEu2BT4Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224018srJ39UbRpfudFLy8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.161719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224018YjrsJQedmMDVHvBU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.965625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224017igNw2K0hPDRfoFHl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.161719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018053122401812hSNuKFgeRC357c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.375000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224031ermxMX843bPzYKCj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.971094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Preludia collection by Carl Hansen &amp; Son &amp; Brad Ascalon </h3><p>丹麦家居品牌 Carl Hansen &amp; Son 推出了其首个办公家具系列 Preludia，与其合作的是美国设计师 Brad Ascalon。可堆叠功能和平板包装的设计，突出其便于运输和收纳的优点。椅子的形态参考了 Carl Hansen 标志性的 20 世纪中期椅子的弯曲结构。</p><p>椅子由数层薄木板壳制成，形成连续弯曲的座椅和靠背。这种 3D 胶合板材质经久耐用，柔软的韧度使其尽可能完美地适应人体曲线，同时保持 Carl Hansen &amp; Son 对于自然材质的尊重。整个系列的椅子由橡木、胡桃木和山毛榉木制成，有的是纯木款，有的装饰有织物、皮革，甚至装上软垫。</p><p>除了主打的椅子之外，Preludia 系列还包括长方形桌子、圆形餐桌以及酒吧桌。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805312241043Sf5JbOBGirzLtwu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.724619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224104vrdRltcAxfUO2mFj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018053122410597iMLwvPIckmzgEf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.380711\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224107m302wPlJ5KsbrR6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224107037HbvrGpzUn5Kw9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224108YAKWrFcQb3hDOBT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224109IkR0FTp8ij5An7wu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.724196\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/05/30/carl-hansen-son-launches-preludia-first-office-furniture-series-brad-ascalon/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Life On Earth Collection by Rooms</h3><p>格鲁吉亚设计二人组 Rooms 推出 Life On Earth 系列家具，包括 12 个由天然石材和符合材料组合而成的 12 个手工制作的物体。</p><p>根据 Rooms 两位创始人 Nata Janberidze 和 Keti Toloraia 的介绍，这些作品参考了他们在格鲁吉亚的童年经历，以及游历亚欧国家的见闻，从前苏联古迹到野兽派建筑，设计师引入了很多建筑设计的细节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224205TEv62DnKjClIqzGp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224206pW5ikyTdRYCNn9ZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224207609BnSt2NIJVsxu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224211I72UiqG5YZ1E3Mxu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224214Jr9G7Ay2u0sqVlWd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224220f86GmSnvxNRjqpcP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224220dly3Ppf9GnAJ0iO2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224230ogxEaiO6ptc819bq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Up Front's bold new brand by Freytag Anderson </h3><p>独立酿酒品牌 Up Front 最近更新了产品包装，请来格拉斯哥设计工作室 Freytag Anderso 操刀包装设计，后者也请来插画家 Stanley Donwood 为其定制设计了插画版包装，灵感来自赫尔曼·梅尔维尔发表于 1851 年的长篇小说《白鲸记》，整个包装围绕《白鲸记》中主人公 Moby Dick 海上冒险的故事来创作，黑白色的对比组合更显高级感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224308WCePj9JxbMHyNa08.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561818\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224308N4o21TyCS93e06xr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224308E0qFufwhUdgbMt5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561818\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224309UZiNDrSJFM1Bu0Pb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224310mIBg6sjtT92nol5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.creativeboom.com/inspiration/up-front-takes-a-bold-brand-position-with-arresting-illustrations-inspired-by-moby-dick/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creative Boom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Egon Side Table by Iratzoki Lizaso for Alki</h3><p>法国高端家具品牌 Alki 为其 Egon 系列再添新品，是一张由设计师 Iratzoki Lizaso 为 Egon 系列量身设计的边桌，配合整个系列的沙发、咖啡桌和靠垫使用。</p><p>Egon 是一款纯实木边桌，体型小巧，易于移动，它既可以是用户相互一杯咖啡闲暇时光的好去处，也可以作为一个可移动的便携式工作站使用。桌子的高度是可以调整的，以满足包括工作、喝咖啡或事吃午餐等不同需求。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224352SaMgGL3q97yBIDuY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.773438\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224352BJeWO5D2vGXfZEbu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.375000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224352JWp5EQ8NwxnVjlUb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.392969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224352RbV7GkHzFZSoxf90.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.191406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224353I7UMJWnsm6akB9o8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.040625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224353uWCXpTwkIUzxHDiS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.595313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/alkis-egon-side-table-will-become-your-handy-sidekick/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Bloom Pencil Case by Ian Bok</h3><p>铅笔盒已经算得上是怀旧产品了，很少出现在成年人的生活领域。但在设计师 Ian Bok 看来，一个好的铅笔盒可以成为提高工作效率的生产力工具，于是他设计了一款名为 Bloom 的铅笔盒，它直立时的高度考虑到了人眼关注到工作台时最舒服的高度，不用从杂乱的桌面中寻找它。</p><p>更特别的是，Bloom 铅笔盒内置磁铁，在关闭时盒身和盖子可以牢固地扣在一起，但打开时，精心设计的角度又将其变成一个开放式笔筒，装饰性和功能性兼而有之。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224447BGORgtbTUhLV96Ix.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224447aeBuHPvOzqEsYm0T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224448Uuynw8JWqFGPv52A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224448DLJuVCQGkE16pcsh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180531224448dsPFgGiXmt8ceUap.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805312244499R6hgEw1FBemPVLd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805312244491JTCxos7UN9VAa2b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/05/31/the-perfect-pencil-case/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}